quran[89]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,"Hɑɑ miim"
  43,2,"M wẽen ne Gaf ( Alkʋrãɑn) vẽnegdgã."
  43,3,"Tõnd maan-a lame t'a yaa Alkʋrãan sẽn yaa larabiindu, sãnd-sãnde y na tall yam."
  43,4,"Ad yẽnda bee gafã ma sẽn be Tõnd nengẽ wã pʋgẽ; a zẽkame n bʋ n manege."
  43,5,"Rẽ yĩnga, Tõnd na n balla Tẽegrã n yi yãmba, tɩ yãmb yɩɩme n yɑɑ neb sẽn ya maan-n-zʋʋg rãmba?"
  43,6,"Lɑ Nabiyaam-rãmb sõor waoog Tõnd sẽn tʋms rẽenem rãmbẽ wã."
  43,7,"Nabiyaam pa yɩ sẽn na n wa b nengẽ, rẽndame tɩ b yɩ n yaand-a."
  43,8,"Tõnd halka sẽn yɩɩd bãmb ne keelem, la rẽenem rãmbã bilgr loogame."
  43,9,"La fo sã n sok-ba: ""ãnd n naan saasã ne Tẽngã?"" B na yeele: ""wilb Naabã sẽn yaa minim Naabã n naan-ba""."
  43,10,"Soab ning sẽn naan-a Tẽngã n kõ yãmbã tɩ yaa sẽn yadge, la A leb n maan soay a pʋgẽ n kõ yãmba sãnd-sãnde yãmb na kãndgã."
  43,11,"Soab ning sẽn sik koomã n yi saasẽ wã ne zemsgo, tɩ Tõnd vɩɩms ne-a tẽng sẽn ki (sẽn kʋɩ), yaa woto bal la b na n yiis yãmba."
  43,12,"Yẽ la Soab ning sẽn naan-a kõbgã fãa gillã, la A naan kogend la rũms n kõ yãmb tɩ y tar n zomd n kẽnda."
  43,13,"Bʋɩl yĩng tɩ yãmb na zomb b poayã zutu, rẽ poorẽ tɩ y tẽeg y Soabã neema-rãmbã; tɩ y sã n wa yõgen n zomb-b bɩ y yeel: ""yɩlgemd be ne Soab ning sẽn nom-a yãoã n kõ tõndã, lɑ tõnd da pa yɩ n na n tõogẽ-yã-a sã n pɑ Wẽnd sẽn wõr n kõ tõndã,"
  43,14,"La Tõnd yaa lεbgdb n tʋgd d Soabã nengẽ""."
  43,15,"La b maan pedg n kõ Wẽnde sẽn yi A yembsã pʋgẽ, ad ninsaal yaa sõm-zɩt sẽn vẽnege."
  43,16,"Bɩ A yãka kom-pugli Yẽ sẽn naanã pʋgẽ la A tũus kom-ribli n kõ yãmba?"
  43,17,"La b sã n noog b yembr fãa sũuri ne bi-buglɑ a sẽn rɩk n kõ Yolsg Naabã, la a nengã sẽn sobgde t'ɑ yaa sũ-toog soaba,"
  43,18,"Ned sẽn wubd nag-teed pʋgẽ n pa tõe n fãag a meng n yi zabd-n-taaga ɑ poglem yĩngɑ lɑ yãmb yet tɩ yɑɑ Wẽnd biigɑ?"
  43,19,"La b yet tɩ malεgs nins sẽn yaa Wẽnd yembsã yaa pagba, rẽ yĩnga bãmb seeda b naoonegã bɩ? B na n gʋlsa b kasetã la b soak-ba."
  43,20,"La b yeele: ""Arrahmaan Naab sã n da ratẽ tõnd ra pa na n tũ-b ye"". B pa tar bãngr baa fʋɩ a pʋgẽ ye, bãmb pa yɩ rẽnda zĩrimbeed pasdb bala."
  43,21,"Bɩ Tõnd kõ-b-la gaf yẽ (Alkʋrãanã) taoore, tɩ bãmb gãd-a?"
  43,22,"Pa woto ye, b yeelame: ""ad tõnd mika d saamb-rãmb dĩin zugu, la tõnd yaa kãndgdb bãmb vũunã zugu."
  43,23,"Yaa woto bala, Tõnd pa tʋms fo taoore bugsd fãa n tʋg tẽngẽ, rẽndame tɩ tẽngã rɩ-n-tɩkã-rãmb yeele: ""tõnd mika d saamb-rãmb tɩ b be dĩin zugu, la tõnd yaa bãmb vũunã tikdba""."
  43,24,"۞T'a (tẽn-tʋʋma) yeele: ""rẽ yĩnga yãmb nɑ kell n tikɑ y sɑɑm-dãmbã bɑ tɩ mam sã n wa yãmb nengẽ ne kãndgr sẽn yɩɩd yãmb sẽn mik y saamb-rãmbã tɩ b tũudẽ wã? "" La b yeel yã: ""tõnd yaa kɩfr-rãmb ne bũmb ning b sẽn tʋms ne yãmbã""."
  43,25,"Tɩ Tõnd na n rol-ba, bɩ f gese yagsdbã baasg yɩ wãn-wãna?"
  43,26,"Tẽeg wakat ning a ɭbraahɩɩm sẽn wa n yeel a saambã ne a nebã: ""ad mam zãaga m meng n yi yãmb sẽn tũudã;"
  43,27,"Sã n pa Soab ning sẽn naan-a maamã, Yẽnda n na n kãndg maam""."
  43,28,"La a maan-a t'a yaa gom-paadg a (ɭbraahɩɩm) pendẽ wã sãnd-sãnde b na lebg n tʋg Wẽnd nengẽ."
  43,29,"Pa woto ye, M wʋmsa bãmb ne b saamb-rãmbã noogo hal tɩ sɩdã wa b nengẽ la tẽn-tʋʋm vẽenegã."
  43,30,"La sɩdã sẽn wa n wa b nengẽ wã, b yeelame: ""yãoã yaa tɩɩm la tõnd kɩfla ne-a""."
  43,31,"La b yeele: ""b ra pa na n sikẽ Alkʋrãan kãngã nin-zɩsg zug sẽn yi tẽmsã a yiibã pʋgẽ (Mak la Toaa'ɩf )""."
  43,32,"Yaa bãmb n pʋɩt fo Soabã yolsgã bɩ? yaa Tõnd n pʋɩ bãmb rɩtlã b sʋk dũni vɩɩmã pʋgẽ, La D zẽk sãnda dargε n yɩɩs sãnda, sẽn na yɩlẽ tɩ sãnda wõr sãnda. La fo Soabã yolsg sõmblem n yɩɩd b sẽn tigimd bũmb ningã."
  43,33,"La sã n pa nebã na n wa yɩ zãma a yembre yĩnga, D na naan n maan tɩ neb nins sẽn kɩfl-b ne Rahmaan Naabã, tɩ b rotã tar bεoongo sẽn yaa wanzuri la rads tɩ b tũud be n rʋʋda."
  43,34,"Tɩ b rotã leb n tar zag-noy la gãt tɩ b kɩl b zutu."
  43,35,"La faas-teedo, la wãnde fãa pa yɩ rẽnda rũni wʋm-noog bala, la laahrã, bee fo Soabã nengẽ, wẽn-zoεtbã yĩnga."
  43,36,"Lɑ ned ning sẽn suusd-a n yi a Rahmaan naaba yʋʋr tẽegre, D togend-a-la ne a Sʋɩtãan tɩ yẽnda yaa a lall-n-taaga,"
  43,37,"La bãmb (Sʋɩtãambã) gɩta nebã n yit sorã, la b tẽedame tɩ b yaa kãndgdba."
  43,38,"Hal t'a (nedã) sã n wa Tõnd nengẽ a yetame: ""M sã n da paamẽ tɩ maam ne foom (Sʋɩtãana) sʋka yaa wala yaang la wĩnto-lʋɩɩngẽ pɑ são! Ad yaa lall-n-ta-wẽnga (la foom a Sʋɩtãana)."
  43,39,"La kõn n tol n naf yãmb rũnda, y sẽn wẽga yĩnga, bala yãmb naaga taab naongã pʋgẽ."
  43,40,"Rẽ yĩnga fo tõe n wʋmsa wʋngɑ, maɑ f nenes zoangɑ, bɩ ned ning sẽn be meneng sẽn vẽneg pʋgẽ?"
  43,41,"Ba tɩ D loog ne foo, ad Tõnd yaa maan-n-roalg rãmba ne-ba."
  43,42,"Mɑɑ tɩ D kɩt tɩ fo yẽnd pʋlen-wẽng ning Tõnd sẽn pʋlem-bã, ad Tõnd tara tõog b zugu."
  43,43,"Bɩ f gãd bũmb ning b sẽn tʋms fo nengẽ wã, ad fo bee so-tɩrg zugu."
  43,44,"La ad a (Alkʋrãanã) yaa zu-zẽkre ne foo la fo nebã, la yɩ bilf bala b na wa n sok yãmb ɑ yelle."
  43,45,"La f sok Tõnd sẽn tʋms-b rãmb sẽn reng fo taoorã: ""rẽ yĩnga Tõnd maana soaben-rãmb zẽng sẽn pa a Rahmaan naab tɩ b tũudẽ?"""
  43,46,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd tʋmsa a Musa ne Tõnd yel-soalmã n tʋg a Fɩr-Aoon la a zamã wã nengẽ, t'a yeele: ""Ad mam yaa bõn-naandsã Soab tẽn-tʋʋma"","
  43,47,"La a sẽn wa n wa bãmb nengẽ ne Tõnd yel-soalm-dãmbã la b sẽn laade."
  43,48,"La Tõnd pa yɩ n na n wilg-b yel-solemd rẽndame tɩ yẽnda bedrem yɩɩda sẽn loog-a wã, Tõnd yõk-b-la ne naongo, sãnd-sãnde b na lebge (n wa Tõnd nengẽ)."
  43,49,"La b yeele: ""foo ɑ tɩɩmã soaba! kos f Soabã tõnd yĩnga (t'A zẽk naongã tõnd zugu) ne A sẽn pʋlem foo tɩ tõnd sã n kõ sɩdã ɑ nɑ n zẽkɑ nɑngã; tɩ ad tõnd nɑ n kãndame t'A sã n zẽk nɑngã""."
  43,50,"La Tõnd sẽn wa n zẽk naongã n yi-bã, la b sẽn yidg al-kaoolã."
  43,51,"T'a fɩr-Aoon moon a zama wã pʋgẽ n yeele: ""yãmb a zamã! Rẽ yĩnga pa maam n so Misra naam, tɩ ko-sood bãmbã yaa sẽn zoet mam tẽngrã, rẽ yĩnga yãmb pa ne sɩda?"
  43,52,"Rẽ yĩnga mam sõmblem pa yɩɩd yãoã sẽn yaa yaalgã, la a pa tõe n gom tɩ fahmã."
  43,53,"Yaa bõe yĩng tɩ b pa na n sik faas-teed a zug sẽn yaa Sãnem, mɑɑ malεgs-rãmbã tong tɑɑbɑ n tũud-a n watẽ?"""
  43,54,"T'a gudg a nebã tɩ b tũ-a, ad-b yɩɩ zãma sẽn yaa dĩin yitba."
  43,55,"La b sẽn wa n sãam Tõnd sũuri, D maan-b lame n role, n bõrb gilli."
  43,56,"Tɩ Tõnd maan-b tɩ b yaa reng-taoor la bilgr ne sẽn wat-b bãmb poorẽ."
  43,57,"La b sẽn wa n rɩk bilgr ne a Maryam biigã, la fo nebã sẽn kilsdi; (n yetẽ tɩ bãmb rʋbsãme pɑ são ɑ ɭɩsɑ ye, b yɑool n tũu yẽ me, rẽnd bãmb ne b rʋbsã sã n yɑɑ bugum rɑgiisi, rẽnd ɑ Mɑryɑm biigɑ me yɑɑ boto)"
  43,58,"La b yeele: ""tõnd soaben-dãmbã sõmblem n yɩɩd bɩ yaa yẽ?"" Bãmbã pa rɩkd bilgr ne foo rẽnda no-koεεm bala. Pa woto ye, bãmb rag n yaa no-keem neba."
  43,59,"Ad ɑ ɭɩsa pa yɩ rẽnda yamb bal Tõnd sẽn maan neema a zugu, la Tõnd maan-a t'a yaa tɑgmɑs ne ɭsrayεl koamba."
  43,60,"La Tõnd sã n sa tʋllẽ D na maan malεgs yãmb zĩigẽ, tɩ b leds yãmb tẽngã poor zugu.( N tũud wẽnd ɑ yembre)"
  43,61,"La ad a (ɭɩsa) yaa tagmas ne dũni wã yikri, bɩ y ra maan sik ne-a ye, la y tũ maam, yãoondã yaa so-tɩrga."
  43,62,"La a Sʋɩtãan ra wa gɩd yãmb dɛ, ad a yaa bε sẽn vẽneg ne yãmba."
  43,63,"La wakat ning a ɭɩsa sẽn wa n wa ne yel-vẽenesã, a yeelame: ""sɩd la hakɩɩka m waa yãmb nengẽ ne bʋʋd sẽn manege; bʋɩl yĩng me tɩ m na vẽneg yãmb yεl sãnda yãmb sẽn yõsd taab a zugu; bɩ y zoe Wẽnd la y tũ maam""."
  43,64,"Ad Wẽnd la mam Soaba, yẽ me la yãmb Soaba; bɩ y tũ-A, ad yãoã la so-tɩrga."
  43,65,"Tɩ sulã yõs taab bãmb ne taab sʋka, la wɩɩbd be ne neb nins sẽn wẽgbã raar ning naong sẽn zabdã."
  43,66,"Rẽ yĩnga b kollda bũmb tɩ sã n pa rũni wã yikr sẽn na n wa b nengẽ ne lingr tɩ b yaool n pa miẽ."
  43,67,"Pa yẽ-to-kõngũs rãmbã yaa beem ne taab ra-kãngã raarã, ralla wẽn-zoεtbã."
  43,68,"Yãmb ɑ Mam yembsã! Yaeesg pa be ne yãmb rũnda ye, la yãmb sũy kõn sãam me ye."
  43,69,"Rãmb nins sẽn kõ sɩd ne Tõnd yel-soalmã, la b yɩ n yɑɑ moeembã;"
  43,70,"Kẽ-y Arzãnã yãmb ne y pagb n kɩdembdẽ."
  43,71,"B gilgda bãmb zug ne sãnem lɑɑse (asεt-rãmbɑ) la ko-toeese; bũmb ning sẽn noom yõor fãa la nin sẽn nong n pid be, tɩ yãmb be a pʋgẽ n yaa paadba."
  43,72,"La yẽ la Arzãn ningã b sẽn kɩt tɩ yãmb rɩk a faad ne bũmb ning yãmb sẽn yɩ n tʋmbdẽ wã yĩngã."
  43,73,"Yãmb tara tɩ-biis wʋsg a pʋgẽ n dɩtẽ."
  43,74,"Ad nin-wẽnsã, bãmb bee gẽhanem naongã pʋgẽ n yaa paadba."
  43,75,"B pa valemd bugmã bãmb zugu, tɩ bãmb be beenẽ tɩ b yaa sẽn wãag b tẽeb ne Wẽnd yolgã."
  43,76,"La Tõnd pa wẽg-b ye, yaa bãmb n da yɩ n yɑɑ wẽgdba."
  43,77,"Tɩ b moon n boole : ""Foo Maaliki, kos f Soabã t'A kʋ tõnd tɩ d peems"", t'a yeel: ""yãmb yaa pɑɑdba "" (pɑɑb sẽn pa tar tεkɑ n pɑ wãagdẽ)."
  43,78,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd waa yãmb nengẽ ne sɩda, la yãmb wʋsg fãa gill kisa sɩda."
  43,79,"Bɩ b rĩnga yelle, rẽnd Tõnd me yaa rĩngdba."
  43,80,"Bɩ b tẽedame tɩ Tõnd pa wʋmb b walengã la b wũnungã? Pa woto ye Tõnd tẽn-tʋʋmbã (Malεgsã) bee b nengẽ n gʋlsdẽ."
  43,81,"Yeele:""Rahmaan Naab sã n da tara biiga, mam na yɩẽ rẽenem n tũ-a""."
  43,82,"Yɩlgemd be ne saas la tẽng Naabã sẽn yaa Al-Ars Naabã n yi bũmb ning bãmb sẽn sɩfdã."
  43,83,"Bɩ f bas-b tɩ b faood la b reemdẽ hal n wa seg raar ning b sẽn pʋlem-bã."
  43,84,"Yẽ n yaa Soab saasẽ, yẽ la Soab tẽng zugu, Yẽ la bʋʋd Naab n le yaa minim Naaba."
  43,85,"La Soab ning bark yɩ wagalle sẽn so-a saas la tẽng naamã la bũmb ning sẽn be b yiibã sʋka; tɩ rũni yikr minimã bee A nengẽ, tɩ yãmb lebgr zĩig yaa Yẽ nengẽ."
  43,86,"La b sẽn kot bũmb nins zẽng tɩ pa tũ ne Wẽndã pa tar sugsgã ye, rẽnda ned ning sẽn seed-a ne sɩd la b miẽ."
  43,87,"Fo sã n sok-ba tɩ ãnd n naan-b b na yete: ""yaa Wẽnde"". La yaa wãn-wãn tɩ bãmb kedgdẽ?"
  43,88,"La M wʋmdɑ (nabiyaamã) koεεgã ɑ sẽn yete: ""m Soabɑ! bãmbã yaa neb sẽn pa kõt sɩda""."
  43,89,"Bɩ f ball n (yaaf ) bas-b la f yeel-b laafɩ koεεga; tɩ sã n yɩ bilf bala b na bãnge."
